#

Savory Stuffed Mushrooms with Cream Cheese and Herbs

35 min
$10
150 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

AmericanItalian

Course:

AppetizerSnack

Tags:

AppetizerQuickSavory

Description

Deliciously savory mushrooms filled with creamy herb-infused cheese, perfect for a quick appetizer!

Ingredients

  • large mushrooms: 12
  • cream cheese: 8 oz
  • garlic: 2 cloves
  • parsley: 2 tbsp
  • chives: 1 tbsp
  • salt: 1/2 tsp
  • pepper: 1/4 tsp
  • olive oil: 1 tbsp
